  verbalize :: a -> String

  verbalize :: Hiding -> String
verbalize = Hiding -> String
hidingToString

instance Verbalize Relevance where
  verbalize :: Relevance -> String
verbalize = \case
      Relevant        {} -> String
"relevant"
      Irrelevant      {} -> String
"irrelevant"
      ShapeIrrelevant {} -> String
"shape-irrelevant"

  verbalize :: Quantity -> String
verbalize = \case
    Quantity0{} -> String

    Quantity1{} -> String
"linear"
    Quantityω{} -> String
"unrestricted"
